---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - Corporate Overview"
  description="Weyland-Yutani Corporation is a British-Japanese multinational conglomerate and the world's leading innovator in terraforming, cybernetics, energy, and interstellar colonization. Founded 2012. Valued at $200T+."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- HERO: THE CORPORATION -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#FFC600] to-transparent"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center py-24">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="h-px w-16 bg-[#FFC600]"></div>
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-mono">EST. OCTOBER 11, 2012</span>
          <div class="h-px w-16 bg-[#FFC600]"></div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl lg:text-[11rem] font-black text-white leading-none uppercase mb-6">
          THE<br/><span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">CORPORATION</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-48 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wider font-mono leading-relaxed">
          A BRITISH-JAPANESE MULTINATIONAL CONGLOMERATE AND THE MOST POWERFUL COMMERCIAL ENTITY IN HUMAN HISTORY
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mt-12">
          <a href="/about/history" class="btn-primary px-10 py-4 text-sm">OUR HISTORY</a>
          <a href="/about/leadership" class="btn-secondary px-10 py-4 text-sm">LEADERSHIP</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 hazard-stripes h-2"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- WHO WE ARE -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-5"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-16 items-start">
            <!-- Left Column: Narrative -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-8">
              <div>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">WHO WE ARE</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-8 uppercase">BUILDING BETTER WORLDS</h2>
              </div>

              <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
                Weyland-Yutani Corporation is a British-Japanese multinational conglomerate headquartered in San Francisco, with major operational centers in Tokyo and the Sea of Tranquility, Luna. We are the world's preeminent leader in terraforming, cybernetics, defense systems, energy production, biological sciences, health technology, and advanced electronics.
              </p>

              <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
                Originally founded as Weyland Corporation on October 11, 2012, by Sir Peter Weyland, the company rapidly became the most innovative and influential enterprise on Earth. Following the historic merger with Yutani Corporation in 2099, the combined entity became the driving force behind humanity's expansion across the stars.
              </p>

              <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
                Today, Weyland-Yutani operates across seven integrated verticals, employs more than half a million people across 47 countries and 300+ colonized worlds, and maintains a market valuation in excess of $200 trillion. Our work touches every aspect of modern civilization, from the atmosphere you breathe to the worlds your children will call home.
              </p>

              <div class="divider-yellow"></div>

              <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-[#FFC600] pl-6 py-2">
                <p class="text-[#FFC600] text-xl font-bold italic font-mono">"IF WE CAN, WE MUST."</p>
                <cite class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-mono mt-2 block not-italic">-- SIR PETER WEYLAND, FOUNDER</cite>
              </blockquote>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Column: Key Facts Card -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-2">
              <div class="corp-card p-0">
                <div class="bg-[#FFC600] px-6 py-4">
                  <h3 class="text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">CORPORATE FACTS</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 space-y-0">
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">FOUNDED</span>
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm font-mono">OCTOBER 11, 2012</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">FOUNDER</span>
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm font-mono">SIR PETER WEYLAND</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">MERGER</span>
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm font-mono">2099 (W-Y FORMED)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">TYPE</span>
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm font-mono">MULTINATIONAL CONGLOMERATE</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">HEADQUARTERS</span>
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm font-mono">SAN FRANCISCO, CA</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">VALUATION</span>
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-sm font-mono">$200T+</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">EMPLOYEES</span>
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm font-mono">500,000+</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">VERTICALS</span>
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm font-mono">7 OPERATIONAL</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4">
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">COLONIES</span>
                    <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-sm font-mono">300+ WORLDS</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- AT A GLANCE: STATS BANNER -->
    <section class="relative bg-[#FFC600] py-16 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
        <div class="industrial-grid-dense w-full h-full"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-black uppercase">AT A GLANCE</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black font-mono mb-1">$200T+</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-black/70 uppercase tracking-widest">MARKET VALUATION</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black font-mono mb-1">500K+</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-black/70 uppercase tracking-widest">EMPLOYEES</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black font-mono mb-1">300+</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-black/70 uppercase tracking-widest">COLONIZED WORLDS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black font-mono mb-1">47</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-black/70 uppercase tracking-widest">COUNTRIES</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black font-mono mb-1">7</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-black/70 uppercase tracking-widest">VERTICALS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black font-mono mb-1">87+</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-black/70 uppercase tracking-widest">YEARS OF INNOVATION</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- OPERATIONAL VERTICALS -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">INTEGRATED OPERATIONS</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">SEVEN VERTICALS.<br/>ONE VISION.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Terraforming -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border-2 border-[#FFC600]/30 clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg font-mono">01</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-3">TERRAFORMING</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Atmospheric processing, ecosystem engineering, and planetary colonization. Making uninhabitable worlds into new homes for humanity.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Cybernetics -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border-2 border-[#FFC600]/30 clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg font-mono">02</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-3">CYBERNETICS & SYNTHETICS</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Development and manufacture of synthetic personnel, cybernetic augmentation, and advanced artificial intelligence systems.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Defense -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border-2 border-[#FFC600]/30 clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg font-mono">03</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-3">SECURITY & DEFENSE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Colonial peacekeeping solutions, defensive systems, weapons manufacturing, and private security operations across all territories.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Energy -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border-2 border-[#FFC600]/30 clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg font-mono">04</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-3">ENERGY SYSTEMS</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Fusion power generation, FTL drive systems, solar harvesting, and advanced energy distribution across interstellar distances.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Health Sciences -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border-2 border-[#FFC600]/30 clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg font-mono">05</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-3">HEALTH SCIENCES</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">MedPod systems, hypersleep technology, pharmaceutical development, and advanced surgical robotics serving billions.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Biological Sciences -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8 group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border-2 border-[#FFC600]/30 clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg font-mono">06</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-3">BIOLOGICAL SCIENCES</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Xenobiology research, genetic engineering, agricultural biotech, and advanced life sciences pushing the frontier of knowledge.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Electronics (span full) -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8 group md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border-2 border-[#FFC600]/30 clip-corner flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg font-mono">07</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-3">ELECTRONICS & COMMUNICATIONS</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">FTL communications infrastructure, shipboard computing systems, navigation technology, and consumer electronics. The backbone of interstellar civilization, connecting 300+ colonized worlds through our proprietary deep-space relay network.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CORPORATE STRUCTURE OVERVIEW -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
            <!-- Structure Text -->
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">CORPORATE STRUCTURE</span>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-8 uppercase">A FRAMEWORK FOR THE FUTURE</h2>

              <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Weyland-Yutani is governed by a Board of Directors and led by a world-class executive team with deep expertise spanning every domain in which we operate. Our organizational structure is designed to maximize integration across our seven verticals while preserving the agility and focused innovation that each demands.
              </p>

              <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                The Corporation operates through a matrix structure that unites geographic and functional leadership. Regional presidents oversee operations in their territories, while vertical heads drive strategy and innovation within their domains. This dual-axis model ensures both global coherence and local responsiveness.
              </p>

              <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
                Our commitment to transparent governance, ethical business practices, and stakeholder value creation has earned us the trust of governments, institutions, and billions of citizens across known space.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Structure Diagram -->
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="terminal">
                <div class="terminal-content">
                  <div class="space-y-3 font-mono text-xs">
                    <div class="text-[#FFC600]">&gt; ORGANIZATIONAL HIERARCHY</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-600">----------------------------------------</div>
                    <div class="text-white">  BOARD OF DIRECTORS</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-500">    |</div>
                    <div class="text-white">    +-- CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-500">    |     |</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- CHIEF OPERATING OFFICER</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- CHIEF FINANCIAL OFFICER</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- CHIEF TECHNOLOGY OFFICER</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- CHIEF SCIENCE OFFICER</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- CHIEF SECURITY OFFICER</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- GENERAL COUNSEL</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-500">    |</div>
                    <div class="text-white">    +-- OPERATIONAL VERTICALS [7]</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-500">    |     |</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- TERRAFORMING OPS</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- CYBERNETICS & SYNTHETICS</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- SECURITY & DEFENSE</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- ENERGY SYSTEMS</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- HEALTH SCIENCES</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- BIOLOGICAL SCIENCES</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">    |     +-- ELECTRONICS & COMMS</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-500">    |</div>
                    <div class="text-white">    +-- REGIONAL OPERATIONS</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">          +-- AMERICAS</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">          +-- EMEA</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">          +-- ASIA-PACIFIC</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-400">          +-- OFF-WORLD</div>
                    <div class="text-gray-600">----------------------------------------</div>
                    <div class="text-[#FFC600]">&gt; STATUS: <span class="status-active">OPERATIONAL</span></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- GLOBAL IMPACT -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">OUR IMPACT</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">SHAPING CIVILIZATION</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg uppercase mb-4">PLANETARY ENGINEERING</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Our atmospheric processors have transformed over 300 barren worlds into habitable environments, creating new homes for billions. Each colonized world represents a triumph of engineering that expands the horizon of human possibility.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-6">
              <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-[#1a1a1a]"></div>
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">300+ WORLDS TRANSFORMED</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg uppercase mb-4">SYNTHETIC INTELLIGENCE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Our David-series synthetics serve alongside humans in every capacity, from scientific research to colonial administration. They represent the pinnacle of artificial intelligence, indistinguishable from their human counterparts.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-6">
              <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-[#1a1a1a]"></div>
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">8 GENERATIONS DEPLOYED</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg uppercase mb-4">FTL TRAVEL</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Faster-than-light propulsion, achieved by Weyland Corp in 2032, collapsed the distances between stars and made interstellar colonization viable. Our fleet of FTL-capable vessels is the largest in operation.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-6">
              <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-[#1a1a1a]"></div>
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">FTL SINCE 2032</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-lg uppercase mb-4">HEALTH & LONGEVITY</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The MedPod 720i and hypersleep technologies have revolutionized medicine and long-duration space travel. Our health sciences division serves billions, extending and improving human life across all territories.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-6">
              <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-[#1a1a1a]"></div>
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">BILLIONS SERVED</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CORPORATE PHILOSOPHY -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-5"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">CORPORATE PHILOSOPHY</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-12 uppercase">THE WEYLAND DOCTRINE</h2>

          <div class="space-y-8 text-left">
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              At the heart of Weyland-Yutani lies a simple, uncompromising belief: that the only limit to human achievement is the willingness to act. Our founder, Sir Peter Weyland, articulated this in the phrase that has guided the Corporation since its inception:
            </p>

            <div class="bg-black border-l-4 border-[#FFC600] p-8 clip-corner">
              <p class="text-[#FFC600] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black italic">"IF WE CAN, WE MUST."</p>
            </div>

            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              This is not mere ambition. It is a moral imperative. When we possess the capability to terraform a dead world into a garden, to cure the incurable, to bridge the void between stars, inaction becomes unconscionable. Weyland-Yutani does not ask whether something should be done. We ask how soon it can be done, and we marshal every resource at our disposal to make it so.
            </p>

            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Our philosophy extends to every employee, from the boardroom to the most distant colony outpost. We cultivate a culture of relentless excellence, intellectual fearlessness, and absolute commitment to the mission of building better worlds.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EXPLORE MORE (Links to Sub-Pages) -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-black border-t-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-2 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white uppercase">EXPLORE THE CORPORATION</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <a href="/about/history" class="corp-card p-8 block group text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:glow-yellow transition-all">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl font-mono">H</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white uppercase mb-2">OUR HISTORY</h3>
